snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Next week, Red Dead Redemption will arrive in stores for Xbox 360® and PlayStation®3.

Today, as the ultimate video before the games release  we present the full-length Official Launch Trailer. 

And dont miss your chance to pre-order your copy now while theres still time to score special pre-order bonus content with participating retailers.

www.rockstargames.com/reddeadredemption/preorder

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood, Intense Violence, Nudity, Strong Language, Strong Sexual Content, Use of Drugs
